title: CLEMENCE, 8 STONE TWO-TONE STRAND NECKLACE, GOLD AND SILVER
description: The Two-Tone Clemence Necklace features a delicate strand of 8 round lab-grown white sapphires bezel-set in sterling silver on an 18k gold vermeil chain. Adjustable by one inch for your preferred fit.
details:
Metal: 18K gold vermeil and sterling silver


Setting: Bezel set


Stone Type: Lab-grown white sapphire


Stone Shape: Round cut


Closure: Spring ring


Chain Length: 16 inches or 17 inches



This necklace includes a loop to adjust the necklace shorter by 1 inch. If you purchase the 16-inch, this includes 15 inches + a 1-inch extension. If you purchase the 17-inch, this includes 16 inches and 1-inch extension.
